{"tid":1604860,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[暗黑防禦魔法]國旗保護罩","createTime":"2019-09-30T05:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T06:06:56.000Z","uid":164378,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"121ae9b80ccfacf28294146c79ed3dd6af1a16b3","tid":1604860,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"尋日又發夢見到一對夫婦向我獻計，話一定要傳比大家! 呢個就係5星旗護體大法。相信大家都聽過外國人好中意用諷刺(sarcastic)既方法玩政治。而今次既新魔法絕對係對準政權。十一國殤 賀佢老母在即，大家有無諗過國殤日比popo一齊普天同慶?<br />\n<br />\n1) 用五星旗蓋tg，大家都知過tg 會著火，popo會幫大家點著5星旗，增加氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n2) 幫popo燒佢地國家國旗/打國旗，只要你身穿5星旗，任何非人物件打你都係辱佢地國家既國旗，到時大家可以一齊大大聲diu7佢辱國🤷🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n3) 最最最緊要係 傳媒，國殤日必定好多外國傳媒，你話如果比佢地影到一大埋旗係國殤日比popo、tg燒，popo打國旗係幾咁令人興奮既事。<br />\n<br />\n最後發夢仙女仲建議我地可以播&quot;榮光&quot;配以tg燒旗做結，一定可以為國殤日係國際上添一分色彩。<br />\n<br />\n以上就係我個夢，希望有高人幫我解下夢，搵者搵多d人一齊幫我解夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ad523b4d99794513447809f5ba4f34494f728a","tid":1604860,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"自推十連 一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46ecd96007a22a54ae8492ffb9ca11032c5a43c","tid":1604860,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:56:27.000Z","msg":"自推十連 二<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910dafa9c0a79f482687e8497ea3b7fc298e1283","tid":1604860,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:58:27.000Z","msg":"自推十連 四<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be2f121e0a727593750e6672a980d011b81e257","tid":1604860,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:59:04.000Z","msg":"自推十連 skip左三<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853da5e78